==English==

===Noun===
'''guarantee'''
# anything that [[assure]]s a certain [[outcome]]
#:''Can you give me a '''guarantee''' that he wil be fit for the match''
# written declaration that a certain product will be fit for a purpose and work correctly
#:''The cooker comes with a 5-year '''guarantee'''.''
# a person who gives such a guarantee; a [[guarantor]]

